sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Penghuni
    participant Sistem
    participant Gateway as Payment Gateway
    participant Basis Data

    Penghuni->>Sistem: Pilih bayar tagihan
    activate Sistem
    Sistem->>Gateway: Request invoice VA
    activate Gateway
    Gateway-->>Sistem: Link/Kode pembayaran
    deactivate Gateway
    Sistem-->>Penghuni: Tampilkan instruksi bayar
    deactivate Sistem
    
    Penghuni->>Gateway: Eksekusi pembayaran
    activate Gateway
    Gateway->>Sistem: Webhook Callback (Sukses)
    deactivate Gateway
    activate Sistem
    Sistem->>Basis Data: Update status invoice = PAID
    activate Basis Data
    Basis Data-->>Sistem: Berhasil
    deactivate Basis Data
    Sistem-->>Penghuni: Notifikasi pelunasan chatbot (faktur digital)
    deactivate Sistem